      "id": "node-driver",
      "title": "Node Execution Driver",
      "description": "This package owns the V8 isolate lifecycle — creating isolates, compiling ESM/CJS, and bridging host capabilities into the sandbox. ModuleAccessFileSystem provides a read-only node_modules overlay that blocks native addons and symlink escapes.",
